  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 46e03a19f8e5e124dad137a0f14696cc, type: 3}
  m_Name: D3FMD
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueHidesSubmit: 1
  lines:
  - 'You remember those rumours I was talking about? '
  - The whole shit about the illness being part of some plan, I got some dirt on
    the whole thing.
  - "Managed to brute force onto a government website through some exploit on the
    messages, couldn\u2019t get to the home page to view the rest of the site though."
  - "We\u2019re thinking this entire town and way of life they\u2019ve created is
    another part of their plan, built up under the noses of every clueless fool living
    here."
  - "Pretty good chance they never even bothered looking for our \u201Ckidnapped
    parents\u201D, and it\u2019s real fucking rich of them to constantly go on about
    \u201Ccreating our own family\u201D, shaming anyone who doesn\u2019t have one
    when they won\u2019t even bring back the ones we deserved, and lost."
  - 'You: I see. But, do you want your own family? One you created by yourself?'
  - "I\u2019m not trying to look like another fucking slave to all that shit they
    feed you, there\u2019s plenty of those lining the streets already. Even if I
    did, not a chance you\u2019d find anyone in here who\u2019d want to be a part
    of that family,  just a whole waste of time to even consider."
  - "Anyways, that\u2019s all I\u2019ve got for now, I\u2019ll get back to you later."
